{"type": "article", "id": 27550, "title": "火山加湿器", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-31T07:01:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 74, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171453hNMRFnHP14gv3mrD.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>谁说水火一定不容？韩国设计师 Dae-hoo Kim 以火山喷发为灵感，设计了这款火山造型的加湿器 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/8875721/VOLCANO\">Volcano</a>。它的造型非常简洁，四种不同的外观分别对应了来自世界各地的知名火山，使用时只需要将水倒入“火山口”即可。除了普通的喷气模式之外，这款火山加湿器还有一个模仿火山喷发的“喷烟圈”模式，这个时候“火山口”还会配合亮起红色的灯光，非常形象。这款产品目前还未投入生产。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171449LXuhAySpv3W5YO1b.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.64259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171450Xz0JiA4D7QtwSkgG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021714510tqNg8JKYyHrMzDL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021714527PnWGlqNaVsdDvyE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64259259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}